The global infusion pump systems, accessories, and software market is segmented by product, type, and application. In terms of products, the market is categorized into devices, accessories, and software. Infusion pump systems play a crucial role in administering fluids, nutrients, and medications into a patient's body in controlled amounts. The different types of infusion pumps available in the market include volumetric infusion pumps, syringe infusion pumps, insulin infusion pumps, enteral infusion pumps, elastomeric infusion pumps, and implantable infusion pumps. These pumps are used across various applications such as diabetes, gastroenterology, analgesia/pain management, pediatrics/neonatology, hematology, and oncology.

